title: Regular Show (Reprise)
description:
Written by Jon Bershad and Avery Monsen

Starring Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, Kelly Hudson, Jonathan Marballi, Langan Kingsley, Jon Bershad, Zack Phillips, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, James McCarthy.

Directed by John Flynn.
Piano by Eric Gersen.

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 13, 2012.

Filmed by Alex Aden.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
